description: Description: 1 set (2 pieces) 13 pieces 5050-SMD LED lights (360 degree design for max lighting output) Simply plug and play THESE ARE NOT SWITCH BACKS. Fitment: This 1157 only replaces 1157 bulbs (aka 2057 2357 7528). Refer to the bulb replacement guide here: Bulb Replacement Guide

description: Description: 1 pair (2 pieces) 13 pieces 5050-SMD LED lights (360 degree design for max lighting output) Simply plug and play Fitment: This 1156 only replaces 1156 bulbs (aka 7506). Refer to the bulb replacement guide here: Bulb Replacement Guide

name: Set of two 6-SMD-5050 1.25" 31mm Festoon LED Bulbs
description: Description: This page features the 6-SMD LED 1.25" 31mm Festoon LED bulbs, perfect for car interior lights, such as map lights, reading lights and dome lights. Fitment This 1.25" 31mm festoon LED bulb will replace the stock DE3175, DE3022, DE3021, 3175, 3022 and 3021 bulbs. - Fits 30-31mm bulbs Refer to the bulb replacement guide here: Bulb Replacement Guide Features: - Dimension: 1.25" 31mm long (Will generally fit 30mm - 31mm housings) - 6 pieces super bright 3-cell 5050 SMD LED lights - The LED bulb is twice as bright as a traditional LED bulb and is 3-4 times brighter than OEM bulb - Perfect for car interior lights, such as map lights, reading lights, and dome lights - This LED bulb is polar sensitive, so in case the bulb won't light up, please flip it 180 degrees Available colors: Xenon White, Ultra Blue, Godzilla Green & Race Red

name: Set of two 6-SMD-5050 1.5" 36mm Festoon LED bulbs
description: Description: This package includes two 6-SMD 1.50" 36mm LED Festoon bulbs, perfect for interior dome lights, reading lights and map lights. Fitment: - This 6-SMD 1.50" 36mm Festoon LED bulb will replace stock 6411, 6413 and 6418 bulbs. - Fits 36-39mm bulbs Refer to the bulb replacement guide here: Bulb Replacement Guide Features - Dimension 1.50" 36mm long (Will fit 36mm - 39mm housings) - 6 pieces super bright 3-Emitter 5050 SMD LED lights - Twice as bright as traditional LED bulbs and 3-4 times brighter than stock bulbs - Perfect for car interior lights, such as dome lights, reading lights and map lights - This LED bulb is polar sensitive, so in case the bulb won't light up, please flip it 180 degrees Available colors: Xenon White, Ultra Blue, Godzilla Green & Race Red

name: Set of two 6-SMD-5050 1.72" 41mm Festoon LED bulbs
description: Description: This package includes two 6-SMD 1.72" 41mm LED Festoon bulbs, perfect for interior dome lights, reading lights and map lights. Fitment: - This 6-SMD 1.72" 41mm Festoon LED bulb will replace stock 578 211-2 212-2 or 214-2 bulbs. - Fits 41-43mm bulbs Refer to the bulb replacement guide here: Bulb Replacement Guide Features - Dimension 1.72" 41mm long (Will fit 41mm - 43mm housings) - 6 pieces super bright 3-Emitter 5050 SMD LED lights - Twice as bright as traditional LED bulbs and 3-4 times brighter than stock bulbs - Perfect for car interior lights, such as dome lights, reading lights and map lights - This LED bulb is polar sensitive, so in case the bulb won't light up, please flip it 180 degrees Available colors: Xenon White, Ultra Blue, Godzilla Green & Race Red

name: Set of two 1W T10 Wedge LED bulbs (White, Green, Red, Blue)
description: Description: Includes two brand new 1W High Power T10 LED bulbs. This High Power LED bulb has length of 0.93 inches and diameter of 0.47 inches which can fit MOST 168, 194, 2825, W5W wedge light housings. Package A pair of 1W High Power T10 LED bulbs. The bulbs will generally fit for the Manufacturer No. W5W, 2825, 2827, 158, 161, 168, or 194, etc. Fitment: - This type of 5-SMD T10 LED bulbs will replace stock bulb sizes: 158 168 175 194 2825 2827 W5W 912 921 Refer to the bulb replacement guide here: Bulb Replacement Guide Available colors: Xenon White, Blue, Green & Red. IMPORTANT: If bulb doesn't light up, simply flip 180 degrees.

name: Set of two 5-SMD T10 Wedge LED bulbs (White, Green, Red, Blue)
description: Description: - This set includes two 5-SMD T10 Wedge LED bulbs. These LED's are 360 degree shine and perfect for car interior lights, door courtesy lights, license plate lights, parking lights or backup reverse lights. Fitment: - This type of 5-SMD T10 LED bulbs will replace stock bulb sizes: 158 168 175 194 2825 2827 W5W 912 921 Refer to the bulb replacement guide here: Bulb Replacement Guide Features: - Dimension: 0.40" in diameter, 1.20" in length 5 pieces of super bright SMD LED lights with 360 degrees shine design - Perfect for car interior lights, map/dome lights, door courtesy lights, license plate lights, parking lights or backup reverse lights Available colors: Xenon White, Blue, Green & Red. IMPORTANT: If bulb doesn't light up, simply flip 180 degrees.
